      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait sorry, what? i think you might have sent the wrong response or something lol. i'm actually trying to study for my structural mechanics exam. can you just explain the actual physics of the moment and the counterbalancing force in the connection point? i need to know how the internal stress resists that rotation.",
